query:
update recurring_events
                set 
                    title = $1,
                    group_id = $2,
                    description = $3,
                    location = $4,
                    event_duration_seconds = $5,
                    recurrence_start = $6,
                    recurrence_end = $7,
                    rrule = $8,
                    last_modified = NOW()
                where id = $9
